name: ERUPTION
description:
Every disaster will surely bring worries and fears. But they don't have to face it alone. We just need to open our eyes, ears even our wallet to give a little hope for them.

This work is part of a charity to help victims of the natural disaster from Mount Semeru eruption, every sale in the first market will be 100% donated to the victims, through sewon NFT #tezos4semeru

2000x2500 pixel
300 dpi
